WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.924 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:01.924 --> 00:00:04.340 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM HENRY: What if there
is a part of ourselves that

00:00:04.340 --> 00:00:06.770 align:middle line:84%
has a bird's eye
view of our lives

00:00:06.770 --> 00:00:08.529 align:middle line:90%
and can see into the future?

00:00:08.529 --> 00:00:10.820 align:middle line:84%
What if you never connected
with that part of yourself,

00:00:10.820 --> 00:00:12.630 align:middle line:90%
then what if you did?

00:00:12.630 --> 00:00:17.250 align:middle line:84%
How different would your life
be if you followed its guidance?

00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:20.908 align:middle line:84%
>>CLARE HENRY: Next on
"Arcanum," The Divine Spark.

00:00:20.908 --> 00:00:23.896 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:23.896 --> 00:00:40.360 align:middle line:90%


00:00:40.360 --> 00:00:42.990 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAM: Let's begin our
investigation into the divine

00:00:42.990 --> 00:00:47.160 align:middle line:84%
spark with some insight
into Gnosticism.

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:51.390 align:middle line:84%
Gnosis means wisdom,
and Gnosticism is really

00:00:51.390 --> 00:00:56.740 align:middle line:84%
a collection of ancient ideas
about awakening or attaining

00:00:56.740 --> 00:00:58.600 align:middle line:90%
enlightened consciousness.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:02.190 align:middle line:84%
Most of what we know about
Gnosticism comes from Egypt.

00:01:02.190 --> 00:01:06.820 align:middle line:84%
In 1945, the Nag Hammadi
library was unexpectedly

00:01:06.820 --> 00:01:10.980 align:middle line:84%
discovered in Egypt, in
a cave in upper Egypt.

00:01:10.980 --> 00:01:15.070 align:middle line:84%
This remarkable collection
of 4th century Coptic texts,

00:01:15.070 --> 00:01:17.620 align:middle line:84%
or Egyptian Christian
texts, are thought

00:01:17.620 --> 00:01:19.990 align:middle line:84%
to have been copied from
material that may date back

00:01:19.990 --> 00:01:23.280 align:middle line:84%
to as early as the second
half of the 1st century.

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:28.850 align:middle line:84%
And it casts new light upon
long obscured Christian history.

00:01:28.850 --> 00:01:31.720 align:middle line:84%
Gnostic views are
diverse; however, they

00:01:31.720 --> 00:01:35.530 align:middle line:84%
agreed on three things:
one, reincarnation,

00:01:35.530 --> 00:01:38.570 align:middle line:84%
the idea that the
soul will transmigrate

00:01:38.570 --> 00:01:42.020 align:middle line:84%
into new bodies from
lifetime to lifetime;

00:01:42.020 --> 00:01:46.410 align:middle line:84%
second, there exists a class
of evil powers called archons,

00:01:46.410 --> 00:01:47.860 align:middle line:84%
and part of our
quest is to learn

00:01:47.860 --> 00:01:52.800 align:middle line:84%
to evade the archons, both
in life and in the afterlife;

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:55.440 align:middle line:84%
thirdly, they believed
in that resurrection

00:01:55.440 --> 00:01:58.730 align:middle line:84%
was possible for
every individual.

00:01:58.730 --> 00:02:01.060 align:middle line:84%
In fact, that is
our ultimate goal.

00:02:01.060 --> 00:02:03.990 align:middle line:84%
We wish to resurrect
from this realm.

00:02:03.990 --> 00:02:08.070 align:middle line:10%
Gnostic theology centered
two additional ideas:

00:02:08.070 --> 00:02:10.880 align:middle line:10%
that a divine spark
dwells within,

00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:12.970 align:middle line:10%
and that the process
of resurrection

00:02:12.970 --> 00:02:15.960 align:middle line:10%
represents a universal
principle-- this means

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:18.710 align:middle line:10%
it happens not just on
earth, but in other realms--

00:02:18.710 --> 00:02:22.660 align:middle line:10%
and that Jesus demonstrated
for humanity the way

00:02:22.660 --> 00:02:27.290 align:middle line:10%
that people, ordinary people,
can ascend and resurrect

00:02:27.290 --> 00:02:31.970 align:middle line:10%
into other realms, into
the divine realm, in fact.

00:02:31.970 --> 00:02:34.130 align:middle line:10%
And in William Blake's
magnificent painting

00:02:34.130 --> 00:02:36.950 align:middle line:10%
of the resurrected
Jesus, we see his divine

00:02:36.950 --> 00:02:42.180 align:middle line:10%
spark illuminated from within,
transforming his entire body

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:43.550 align:middle line:10%
into light.

00:02:43.550 --> 00:02:47.830 align:middle line:10%
"The Resurrection" from 1805
is one of Blake's masterpieces

00:02:47.830 --> 00:02:49.880 align:middle line:10%
among many.

00:02:49.880 --> 00:02:54.290 align:middle line:10%
Another is his painting "Michael
Foretells the Crucifixion,"

00:02:54.290 --> 00:02:58.620 align:middle line:10%
where Blake again emphasizes
that Jesus shows the way

00:02:58.620 --> 00:03:01.750 align:middle line:10%
to light the candle
within, if you will,

00:03:01.750 --> 00:03:07.330 align:middle line:10%
ignite the divine spark, and
transform the body into light.

00:03:07.330 --> 00:03:11.840 align:middle line:10%
In other words, to resurrect the
body from the material plane.

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:15.160 align:middle line:10%
Gnostics believe that in
order to achieve salvation,

00:03:15.160 --> 00:03:17.620 align:middle line:10%
or resurrection,
one must possess

00:03:17.620 --> 00:03:20.800 align:middle line:10%
a certain knowledge,
or gnosis, which

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:24.730 align:middle line:10%
must be delivered to a person
by a messenger of light.

00:03:24.730 --> 00:03:26.840 align:middle line:10%
Now this gives us all
hope, because we don't all

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:30.280 align:middle line:10%
have to know exactly
everything about resurrection.

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:32.580 align:middle line:84%
We just need to
know enough to come

00:03:32.580 --> 00:03:36.190 align:middle line:84%
on the radar of a messenger
of light, who will assist us

00:03:36.190 --> 00:03:38.110 align:middle line:90%
in our transformation.

00:03:38.110 --> 00:03:41.420 align:middle line:10%
This literature is
called apocalyptic.

00:03:41.420 --> 00:03:44.880 align:middle line:10%
And what that means is
it's revelatory literature

00:03:44.880 --> 00:03:49.160 align:middle line:10%
in which revelation,
or gnosis, is delivered

00:03:49.160 --> 00:03:53.640 align:middle line:10%
to a human recipient by an
otherworldly or supernatural

00:03:53.640 --> 00:03:54.690 align:middle line:10%
being.

00:03:54.690 --> 00:03:58.540 align:middle line:10%
This revelation discloses
a transcendent reality,

00:03:58.540 --> 00:04:00.990 align:middle line:10%
or a supernatural world.

00:04:00.990 --> 00:04:02.770 align:middle line:10%
So we're talking
about the Gnostics

00:04:02.770 --> 00:04:05.350 align:middle line:10%
recognizing that there
are these messenger

00:04:05.350 --> 00:04:08.380 align:middle line:10%
beings, celestial beings,
otherworldly supernatural

00:04:08.380 --> 00:04:11.590 align:middle line:10%
beings, who can enter
into our consciousness

00:04:11.590 --> 00:04:16.019 align:middle line:10%
and assist us in completing our
earthly mission of attaining

00:04:16.019 --> 00:04:17.779 align:middle line:10%
the resurrection body.

00:04:17.779 --> 00:04:20.779 align:middle line:10%
An example of this
literature is the "Apocalypse

00:04:20.779 --> 00:04:25.200 align:middle line:10%
of Abraham," which describes
a celestial being named Jaeol,

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:27.810 align:middle line:10%
who some believe is actually
Yahweh, the Old Testament

00:04:27.810 --> 00:04:31.620 align:middle line:10%
God, an angel who lived
in the seventh heaven

00:04:31.620 --> 00:04:33.430 align:middle line:10%
and was sent to
Abraham to reveal

00:04:33.430 --> 00:04:36.960 align:middle line:10%
the history of his people
and was also sent to Daniel,

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:39.960 align:middle line:10%
who lived in Babylon during
the Old Testament times.

00:04:39.960 --> 00:04:43.480 align:middle line:10%
So here is this
remarkable angel Jaeol,

00:04:43.480 --> 00:04:47.210 align:middle line:10%
who is shown with this
rainbow ring round his body.

00:04:47.210 --> 00:04:50.710 align:middle line:10%
This is based upon the
description in the "Apocalypse

00:04:50.710 --> 00:04:54.040 align:middle line:10%
of Abraham" that tells us that
the appearance of this being's

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:57.120 align:middle line:10%
body was like sapphire,
the look of his countenance

00:04:57.120 --> 00:05:00.590 align:middle line:10%
like chrysolite, and the
hair of his head like snow,

00:05:00.590 --> 00:05:04.930 align:middle line:10%
with a turban upon his head like
the appearance of a rainbow.

00:05:04.930 --> 00:05:09.050 align:middle line:10%
This is yet another example
of a rainbow-like being,

00:05:09.050 --> 00:05:12.780 align:middle line:10%
where a celestial being
possessing a rainbow body that

00:05:12.780 --> 00:05:17.160 align:middle line:10%
manifests on the Earth plane
and delivers cosmic knowledge.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:20.870 align:middle line:84%
So here's the detail of Jaeol
with this shimmering or shining

00:05:20.870 --> 00:05:23.450 align:middle line:84%
face, this rainbow
ring around its head,

00:05:23.450 --> 00:05:27.620 align:middle line:84%
indicating that this is a
being of rainbow body light.

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:30.430 align:middle line:84%
This being is delivering
sacred knowledge

00:05:30.430 --> 00:05:34.250 align:middle line:84%
to Abraham, who is
consuming that knowledge.

00:05:34.250 --> 00:05:36.460 align:middle line:90%
He's eating this book.

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:38.830 align:middle line:84%
John the Revelator
also did the same thing

00:05:38.830 --> 00:05:41.260 align:middle line:84%
when an angel
manifested before him.

00:05:41.260 --> 00:05:44.640 align:middle line:84%
John ate the heavenly
book that contained

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:48.430 align:middle line:84%
the Gnostic knowledge
of ascension.

00:05:48.430 --> 00:05:52.150 align:middle line:84%
This messenger is a helper
that descends from above

00:05:52.150 --> 00:05:57.120 align:middle line:84%
and is considered actually
our heavenly light twin.

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:58.390 align:middle line:90%
Now think about that.

00:05:58.390 --> 00:06:01.340 align:middle line:84%
What they're suggesting is
that our earthly body is,

00:06:01.340 --> 00:06:05.160 align:middle line:84%
in a sense, a sort of a puppet
on a string of this more

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:10.610 align:middle line:84%
magnificent, evolved aspect
of ourselves, our higher self.

00:06:10.610 --> 00:06:14.270 align:middle line:84%
And by linking with it,
we're able to download

00:06:14.270 --> 00:06:18.520 align:middle line:84%
this sacred knowledge that we
need to complete our ascension.

00:06:18.520 --> 00:06:21.990 align:middle line:84%
Every soul has a
messenger of light.

00:06:21.990 --> 00:06:24.820 align:middle line:90%
Every soul has a higher self.

00:06:24.820 --> 00:06:26.430 align:middle line:84%
And part of our
quest is to learn

00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:29.870 align:middle line:84%
to link with that
aspect of ourselves.

00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:32.410 align:middle line:84%
I believe it's what
brought you here today

00:06:32.410 --> 00:06:36.890 align:middle line:84%
to watch this program, to absorb
this knowledge at this time.

00:06:36.890 --> 00:06:39.780 align:middle line:84%
By being here, it says
you're ready to make

00:06:39.780 --> 00:06:42.330 align:middle line:84%
the link with this
aspect of yourself.

00:06:42.330 --> 00:06:45.320 align:middle line:84%
You're ready to get
the message, to receive

00:06:45.320 --> 00:06:47.790 align:middle line:90%
the download in other words.

00:06:47.790 --> 00:06:50.490 align:middle line:84%
"If you want to know your Higher
Self," said Rudolf Steiner,

00:06:50.490 --> 00:06:53.450 align:middle line:84%
"look at the people you've
met in the last year."

00:06:53.450 --> 00:06:55.660 align:middle line:84%
Who are you calling
into your life that

00:06:55.660 --> 00:06:59.180 align:middle line:84%
will help you to
complete your ascension?

00:06:59.180 --> 00:07:02.080 align:middle line:84%
Powerful, powerful
idea from Mr. Steiner.

00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:04.915 align:middle line:84%
I was once in Florida giving a
presentation on this subject,

00:07:04.915 --> 00:07:07.077 align:middle line:84%
and I asked the audience,
hey, have you ever

00:07:07.077 --> 00:07:08.410 align:middle line:90%
connected with your higher self?

00:07:08.410 --> 00:07:10.850 align:middle line:84%
And how do you know
when it's your higher

00:07:10.850 --> 00:07:12.230 align:middle line:90%
self that's speaking to you?

00:07:12.230 --> 00:07:13.900 align:middle line:90%
Your messenger self?

00:07:13.900 --> 00:07:16.860 align:middle line:84%
And a woman-- I'll never forget
her answer-- she said, whenever

00:07:16.860 --> 00:07:20.330 align:middle line:84%
I'm in a time of crisis
or perhaps afraid,

00:07:20.330 --> 00:07:22.130 align:middle line:84%
the voice always
asks, what would

00:07:22.130 --> 00:07:25.370 align:middle line:90%
you do if you weren't afraid?

00:07:25.370 --> 00:07:28.380 align:middle line:84%
Remember the message of the
transfiguration from Jesus.

00:07:28.380 --> 00:07:31.330 align:middle line:90%
Rise and do not be afraid.

00:07:31.330 --> 00:07:35.160 align:middle line:84%
It seems that that's our number
one mission on the Gnostic path

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:38.400 align:middle line:84%
is to overcome fear,
to leave that behind,

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:42.600 align:middle line:84%
and act is if, not that we're
fearless, but rather, that we

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:45.390 align:middle line:90%
are fully empowered beings.

00:07:45.390 --> 00:07:47.630 align:middle line:84%
What would you do if
you weren't afraid?

00:07:47.630 --> 00:07:50.560 align:middle line:84%
What would you do if you
knew you would always

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:52.570 align:middle line:90%
have the highest success?

00:07:52.570 --> 00:07:54.940 align:middle line:84%
What new decisions or
choices would you make?

00:07:54.940 --> 00:07:57.320 align:middle line:84%
What things would you
do that perhaps you've

00:07:57.320 --> 00:07:58.949 align:middle line:90%
procrastinated on?

00:07:58.949 --> 00:08:00.990 align:middle line:84%
Maybe part of the message
of this program for you

00:08:00.990 --> 00:08:04.570 align:middle line:84%
now is to-- to get on to
those things, to do it now,

00:08:04.570 --> 00:08:07.550 align:middle line:84%
and to act as if you
are fully empowered.

00:08:07.550 --> 00:08:09.170 align:middle line:90%
And then you will be.

00:08:09.170 --> 00:08:11.570 align:middle line:90%
Could be as simple as that.

00:08:11.570 --> 00:08:14.560 align:middle line:84%
"What you're looking for,"
said St. Francis of Assisi,

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:15.940 align:middle line:90%
"is what is looking."

00:08:15.940 --> 00:08:18.210 align:middle line:84%
In other words,
that messenger self

00:08:18.210 --> 00:08:20.530 align:middle line:84%
is ever present in
our consciousness.

00:08:20.530 --> 00:08:23.460 align:middle line:84%
And while we're
seeking its guidance,

00:08:23.460 --> 00:08:26.210 align:middle line:84%
it's also what is
looking at us and trying

00:08:26.210 --> 00:08:27.730 align:middle line:90%
to communicate with us.

00:08:27.730 --> 00:08:31.170 align:middle line:84%
So what you are looking
for is what is looking,

00:08:31.170 --> 00:08:33.390 align:middle line:90%
another profound message.

00:08:33.390 --> 00:08:36.370 align:middle line:84%
This story is reflected
in a Slavonic tale

00:08:36.370 --> 00:08:37.890 align:middle line:90%
called "The Ladder of Jacob."

00:08:37.890 --> 00:08:42.780 align:middle line:84%
It's a variation on the book
of Genesis' story of Jacob, who

00:08:42.780 --> 00:08:46.080 align:middle line:84%
fell asleep and laid his head
on the Philosopher's Stone

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:49.210 align:middle line:84%
and saw the ladder ascending
into the heavens with angels

00:08:49.210 --> 00:08:51.480 align:middle line:84%
ascending and descending
on either side.

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:55.110 align:middle line:84%
In the Slavonic version,
Jacob sees an angel

00:08:55.110 --> 00:08:58.960 align:middle line:84%
named Sariel, who
instructs Jacob regarding

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:01.190 align:middle line:90%
the sacred secrets of heaven.

00:09:01.190 --> 00:09:04.510 align:middle line:84%
He's communicating with his
messenger self, in other words.

00:09:04.510 --> 00:09:06.970 align:middle line:84%
And what happens in the
stories, at the conclusion

00:09:06.970 --> 00:09:10.280 align:middle line:84%
of this instruction, Jacob
is given the knowledge

00:09:10.280 --> 00:09:15.650 align:middle line:84%
that he has a heavenly
identity, just like we all do,

00:09:15.650 --> 00:09:18.900 align:middle line:84%
that his celestial
self, his star self,

00:09:18.900 --> 00:09:22.630 align:middle line:84%
is truly a great, luminous
being, probably a rainbow

00:09:22.630 --> 00:09:26.240 align:middle line:84%
body being, who serves
before the face of God.

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:29.510 align:middle line:84%
And this aspect of ourselves,
our Earthly self, again,

00:09:29.510 --> 00:09:32.080 align:middle line:84%
is just a-- sort of like
the puppet on the string

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.920 align:middle line:84%
that's here to
explore earth life,

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:37.210 align:middle line:84%
perhaps to work out karma,
to learn certain things,

00:09:37.210 --> 00:09:39.900 align:middle line:84%
or, in the deepest
Gnostic sense,

00:09:39.900 --> 00:09:44.340 align:middle line:84%
to serve as an
agent of God's love.

00:09:44.340 --> 00:09:48.810 align:middle line:10%
That's why we're here is to
learn to love to the greatest

00:09:48.810 --> 00:09:51.560 align:middle line:10%
extent that we possibly can.

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:53.880 align:middle line:10%
To receive the knowledge
from the higher self

00:09:53.880 --> 00:09:58.660 align:middle line:10%
requires, obviously, that we
let go of fear and embrace love,

00:09:58.660 --> 00:10:02.300 align:middle line:10%
but also that we must
be trying to be reaching

00:10:02.300 --> 00:10:06.220 align:middle line:10%
beyond the evil, dark,
material, physical earth body

00:10:06.220 --> 00:10:09.430 align:middle line:10%
and towards that of the
good, light, immaterial,

00:10:09.430 --> 00:10:11.160 align:middle line:10%
and spiritual worlds.

00:10:11.160 --> 00:10:14.990 align:middle line:10%
So much of our time is
spent serving the material

00:10:14.990 --> 00:10:17.890 align:middle line:10%
world rather than
the immaterial.

00:10:17.890 --> 00:10:21.080 align:middle line:84%
I often ask people
when they're working

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:25.070 align:middle line:84%
in the spiritual realms,
what is your exit strategy?

00:10:25.070 --> 00:10:27.220 align:middle line:84%
And by that I mean
where are you going

00:10:27.220 --> 00:10:30.240 align:middle line:84%
to go when you leave
the earth plane?

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:32.700 align:middle line:84%
And how are you
going to get there?

00:10:32.700 --> 00:10:34.620 align:middle line:90%
What's your exit strategy?

00:10:34.620 --> 00:10:36.340 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we often
spend so much more

00:10:36.340 --> 00:10:38.810 align:middle line:84%
of our time focusing
on our 401(k)

00:10:38.810 --> 00:10:43.130 align:middle line:84%
than we focus on where we're
going from here in eternity.

00:10:43.130 --> 00:10:46.520 align:middle line:84%
Because Earth life is a
blink of eye, as they say,

00:10:46.520 --> 00:10:49.520 align:middle line:84%
and our eternal self
will be spending time

00:10:49.520 --> 00:10:51.170 align:middle line:90%
in eternity in the cosmos.

00:10:51.170 --> 00:10:53.590 align:middle line:84%
But yet on Earth, we
don't think too much

00:10:53.590 --> 00:10:56.530 align:middle line:84%
about that aspect of our
lives and that realm.

00:10:56.530 --> 00:10:58.470 align:middle line:84%
But the Gnostics
are encouraging us

00:10:58.470 --> 00:11:03.000 align:middle line:84%
to do so because, in doing so,
we broaden our perspective,

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.430 align:middle line:90%
open up our spectrum.

00:11:04.430 --> 00:11:06.460 align:middle line:84%
We're focused on
that one channel,

00:11:06.460 --> 00:11:10.220 align:middle line:84%
listening to that same song over
and over again, when there's

00:11:10.220 --> 00:11:14.660 align:middle line:84%
a whole other range or spectrum
of frequency and vibration,

00:11:14.660 --> 00:11:18.050 align:middle line:84%
tones and tunes out here
that we can tap into just

00:11:18.050 --> 00:11:23.100 align:middle line:84%
by opening up our hearts and
minds to the immaterial realm.

00:11:23.100 --> 00:11:26.020 align:middle line:84%
The following Gnostic
story is offered

00:11:26.020 --> 00:11:29.640 align:middle line:84%
as a bit of a meditation, and
it would be OK at this point

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:33.100 align:middle line:84%
if you just took a deep
breath, closed your eyes,

00:11:33.100 --> 00:11:36.795 align:middle line:84%
and for the next moment or so,
think deeply about the words

00:11:36.795 --> 00:11:37.670 align:middle line:90%
that I'm saying here.

00:11:37.670 --> 00:11:39.086 align:middle line:84%
Because what I'm
going to offer to

00:11:39.086 --> 00:11:41.880 align:middle line:84%
you is what's called
the Gnostic call.

00:11:41.880 --> 00:11:45.090 align:middle line:84%
In other words, this is when
the Gnostics would invite

00:11:45.090 --> 00:11:49.440 align:middle line:84%
new initiates into their
schools, their mystery schools,

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:51.970 align:middle line:84%
this is the story
they would tell them.

00:11:51.970 --> 00:11:54.930 align:middle line:84%
And it serves as
sort of a guideline

00:11:54.930 --> 00:11:58.310 align:middle line:84%
or an outline of
our earthly mission.

00:11:58.310 --> 00:11:59.060 align:middle line:90%
So here it goes.

00:11:59.060 --> 00:12:00.620 align:middle line:84%
It's a Gnostic
story that's based

00:12:00.620 --> 00:12:03.050 align:middle line:84%
on the Gnostic
Hymn of the Pearl.

00:12:03.050 --> 00:12:06.680 align:middle line:84%
And it's also found in the
Nag Hammadi library in Egypt

00:12:06.680 --> 00:12:09.400 align:middle line:84%
and, as I said, is referred
to as the Gnostic call.

00:12:09.400 --> 00:12:10.920 align:middle line:90%
So here it goes.

00:12:10.920 --> 00:12:14.760 align:middle line:84%
Imagine you are a
prince or a princess.

00:12:14.760 --> 00:12:16.880 align:middle line:84%
One day, your parents,
the king and queen,

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:19.180 align:middle line:84%
send you on a mission
to Egypt, which

00:12:19.180 --> 00:12:21.430 align:middle line:84%
symbolizes Earth
life in this case.

00:12:21.430 --> 00:12:25.080 align:middle line:84%
You must find a pearl
guarded by a hungry dragon.

00:12:25.080 --> 00:12:28.110 align:middle line:84%
You take off your royal robe,
your light garment that's

00:12:28.110 --> 00:12:30.820 align:middle line:84%
shimmering with jewels,
and you leave the kingdom

00:12:30.820 --> 00:12:33.740 align:middle line:84%
of your parents, which
is in a celestial realm.

00:12:33.740 --> 00:12:37.020 align:middle line:84%
You journey into Egypt,
putting on dirty clothing

00:12:37.020 --> 00:12:39.730 align:middle line:84%
and disguising yourself
as an Egyptian.

00:12:39.730 --> 00:12:42.510 align:middle line:84%
But somehow, the
Egyptians discover

00:12:42.510 --> 00:12:44.030 align:middle line:90%
that you're a foreigner.

00:12:44.030 --> 00:12:48.150 align:middle line:84%
They give you food that makes
you forget your royal birth.

00:12:48.150 --> 00:12:52.430 align:middle line:84%
You forget that you're a star
child temporarily inhabiting

00:12:52.430 --> 00:12:53.370 align:middle line:90%
this realm.

00:12:53.370 --> 00:12:56.680 align:middle line:84%
And this food makes you believe
that you're one of them.

00:12:56.680 --> 00:13:01.130 align:middle line:84%
And you sink into a
deep, forgetful sleep.

00:13:01.130 --> 00:13:03.580 align:middle line:84%
Your parents see
your plight, and they

00:13:03.580 --> 00:13:06.950 align:middle line:84%
send you a letter that
tells you to awaken.

00:13:06.950 --> 00:13:09.550 align:middle line:84%
As a matter of fact, the letter
is written in your heart,

00:13:09.550 --> 00:13:11.360 align:middle line:84%
according to the
Hymn of the Pearl.

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:15.450 align:middle line:84%
It reminds you of your quest
to recover the pearl, which

00:13:15.450 --> 00:13:18.830 align:middle line:84%
is the Philosopher's Stone,
the Chintamani stone.

00:13:18.830 --> 00:13:20.760 align:middle line:84%
And then suddenly,
you remember who

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:24.760 align:middle line:84%
you are, a child of
kings, a royal child

00:13:24.760 --> 00:13:27.040 align:middle line:90%
from the celestial realms.

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:30.320 align:middle line:84%
And you quickly, then,
subdue the dragon

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:32.140 align:middle line:84%
and recover the
pearl and depart,

00:13:32.140 --> 00:13:35.610 align:middle line:84%
leaving behind your dirty
clothing, your Earthly

00:13:35.610 --> 00:13:36.850 align:middle line:90%
clothing.

00:13:36.850 --> 00:13:41.900 align:middle line:10%
And what happens
next is you then

00:13:41.900 --> 00:13:46.030 align:middle line:10%
return to your native
land, the celestial realms,

00:13:46.030 --> 00:13:49.950 align:middle line:10%
and you see your shimmering,
royal robe, your light body

00:13:49.950 --> 00:13:52.720 align:middle line:10%
garment, which reminds
you of the splendor

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:55.540 align:middle line:10%
you lived in before,
your original home.

00:13:55.540 --> 00:13:57.530 align:middle line:10%
The garment speaks
to you, telling you

00:13:57.530 --> 00:13:58.990 align:middle line:10%
that it belongs
to the one who is

00:13:58.990 --> 00:14:01.550 align:middle line:10%
stronger than all human beings.

00:14:01.550 --> 00:14:04.460 align:middle line:10%
And now you put on your
royal robe once more,

00:14:04.460 --> 00:14:07.720 align:middle line:10%
and you return to
your father's palace.

00:14:07.720 --> 00:14:10.790 align:middle line:84%
The king and queen, of
course, symbolize the creator

00:14:10.790 --> 00:14:12.490 align:middle line:84%
and a feminine
being the Gnostics

00:14:12.490 --> 00:14:17.110 align:middle line:84%
called the holy mother,
or Sophia, or wisdom.

00:14:17.110 --> 00:14:20.660 align:middle line:84%
Their kingdom is a realm of
light, a place totally outside

00:14:20.660 --> 00:14:22.890 align:middle line:90%
of matter as we know it.

00:14:22.890 --> 00:14:26.770 align:middle line:84%
It's spoken of as the
pleroma, or fullness.

00:14:26.770 --> 00:14:30.220 align:middle line:84%
Some believe it's the center
of the Milky Way galaxy.

00:14:30.220 --> 00:14:32.850 align:middle line:84%
Your royal robe,
the shimmering robe,

00:14:32.850 --> 00:14:37.920 align:middle line:84%
that represents your true self,
your divine lineage and image.

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:41.640 align:middle line:84%
The dirty clothing represents
your Earthly body, your Earthly

00:14:41.640 --> 00:14:43.480 align:middle line:84%
matter body, which
you donned when

00:14:43.480 --> 00:14:46.980 align:middle line:84%
you entered Egypt,
the material world.

00:14:46.980 --> 00:14:49.680 align:middle line:84%
So this expresses
for us this idea

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:53.430 align:middle line:84%
that we're originally celestial
light beings who temporarily

00:14:53.430 --> 00:14:56.740 align:middle line:84%
inhabit one of these
earthly vehicles.

00:14:56.740 --> 00:15:00.240 align:middle line:84%
And our ultimate mission
is to recall who we truly

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:04.860 align:middle line:84%
are as celestial beings and
reclaim that garment of light.

00:15:04.860 --> 00:15:08.370 align:middle line:84%
When you descended into the
Earth plane into mortality,

00:15:08.370 --> 00:15:11.220 align:middle line:84%
you left behind
your divine image.

00:15:11.220 --> 00:15:14.410 align:middle line:84%
You forgot who you
truly were, and you

00:15:14.410 --> 00:15:17.310 align:middle line:90%
became an incomplete person.

00:15:17.310 --> 00:15:21.550 align:middle line:10%
You fell asleep when you
forgot your true origin.

00:15:21.550 --> 00:15:25.610 align:middle line:10%
And the message sent by your
parents represents the savior.

00:15:25.610 --> 00:15:27.740 align:middle line:10%
He will awaken you,
this messenger,

00:15:27.740 --> 00:15:29.420 align:middle line:10%
and will remind
you what you must

00:15:29.420 --> 00:15:34.550 align:middle line:10%
do: recover the pearl, that
divine spark within your soul,

00:15:34.550 --> 00:15:37.420 align:middle line:10%
find your way back to
the realm of the light,

00:15:37.420 --> 00:15:42.370 align:middle line:10%
and clothe yourself once more
in your royal light garment.

00:15:42.370 --> 00:15:46.970 align:middle line:84%
In other words, reintegrate
with your divine image.

00:15:46.970 --> 00:15:51.270 align:middle line:84%
This is the message of the
Gnostics, the Gnostic call.

00:15:51.270 --> 00:15:55.300 align:middle line:10%
And by recovering your soul and
reintegrating with the divine,

00:15:55.300 --> 00:15:59.960 align:middle line:10%
remembering yourself as in
the Egyptian story of Osiris,

00:15:59.960 --> 00:16:04.350 align:middle line:10%
you will have achieved
gnosis, or knowledge, awakened

00:16:04.350 --> 00:16:07.500 align:middle line:10%
conscience-- consciousness,
enlightenment,

00:16:07.500 --> 00:16:10.575 align:middle line:10%
which is salvation
in the gnostic sense.

00:16:10.575 --> 00:16:13.260 align:middle line:10%
It's something you
must do for yourself,

00:16:13.260 --> 00:16:16.400 align:middle line:10%
and only you can
do for yourself.

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:18.250 align:middle line:10%
For the Gnostics,
achieving gnosis

00:16:18.250 --> 00:16:21.150 align:middle line:10%
meant to know oneself as God.

00:16:21.150 --> 00:16:24.570 align:middle line:84%
Know thyself is
the key inscription

00:16:24.570 --> 00:16:26.630 align:middle line:90%
over the temple of Delphi.

00:16:26.630 --> 00:16:29.560 align:middle line:84%
That's the primary
Gnostic inscription.

00:16:29.560 --> 00:16:33.200 align:middle line:10%
Know thyself as a divine being.

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:37.540 align:middle line:10%
But to know meant not merely to
understand one's divine origin,

00:16:37.540 --> 00:16:42.260 align:middle line:10%
but to achieve the classic goal
of the mystic union with God.

00:16:42.260 --> 00:16:44.580 align:middle line:10%
That is our ultimate goal.

00:16:44.580 --> 00:16:47.360 align:middle line:84%
And putting on the royal
garment and recovering the pearl

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:49.430 align:middle line:84%
are just some of
the images Gnostics

00:16:49.430 --> 00:16:54.230 align:middle line:84%
used to describe
achieving gnosis.

00:16:54.230 --> 00:16:56.950 align:middle line:10%
According to one gnostic
myth, the shaping

00:16:56.950 --> 00:16:58.800 align:middle line:10%
of the material
world was the result

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:01.500 align:middle line:10%
of Sophia, who is
often described

00:17:01.500 --> 00:17:04.410 align:middle line:10%
as an emanation
of eternal light,

00:17:04.410 --> 00:17:08.819 align:middle line:10%
light beyond light, coming
from beyond the material world,

00:17:08.819 --> 00:17:12.040 align:middle line:10%
an immaculate mirror
of God's activity,

00:17:12.040 --> 00:17:16.410 align:middle line:10%
and as the spouse of the
Lord, say the Gnostic texts.

00:17:16.410 --> 00:17:19.980 align:middle line:90%
She's visualized as a goddess.

00:17:19.980 --> 00:17:22.930 align:middle line:10%
Here's an icon of
Sophia from Russia

00:17:22.930 --> 00:17:25.079 align:middle line:10%
in the late 16th
century, where we

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:28.870 align:middle line:10%
see Sophia enthroned
with Mary and John

00:17:28.870 --> 00:17:31.760 align:middle line:10%
the Baptist and the baby
Jesus on either side.

00:17:31.760 --> 00:17:36.110 align:middle line:10%
We see the familiar imagery
of the portal, or the gateway.

00:17:36.110 --> 00:17:40.850 align:middle line:10%
It could actually be an image
of the divine pearl as well.

00:17:40.850 --> 00:17:44.800 align:middle line:10%
In another example, we see
Sophia enthroned once again,

00:17:44.800 --> 00:17:48.370 align:middle line:10%
and it illustrates the
concept of personifying Wisdom

00:17:48.370 --> 00:17:51.450 align:middle line:10%
as a deity, as a
feminine deity, that

00:17:51.450 --> 00:17:53.320 align:middle line:10%
was familiar to the Romans.

00:17:53.320 --> 00:17:55.900 align:middle line:10%
They got this from the Greeks
and the Greek philosophy

00:17:55.900 --> 00:18:00.180 align:middle line:10%
and the mystery religions of
the Near East of Egypt, of Iran

00:18:00.180 --> 00:18:04.150 align:middle line:10%
and Iraq, where these
concepts were proliferated

00:18:04.150 --> 00:18:08.410 align:middle line:10%
and were ultimately synthesized
by the Jewish mystics,

00:18:08.410 --> 00:18:12.230 align:middle line:10%
known as the Essenes, who
lived in Alexandria, Egypt,

00:18:12.230 --> 00:18:15.680 align:middle line:10%
in Jerusalem, and ultimately
moved to Qumran in the Holy

00:18:15.680 --> 00:18:16.430 align:middle line:10%
Land.

00:18:16.430 --> 00:18:19.210 align:middle line:10%
For Christian theologians,
its legitimacy

00:18:19.210 --> 00:18:21.050 align:middle line:10%
was endorsed in
the opening verses

00:18:21.050 --> 00:18:23.550 align:middle line:10%
of the ninth chapter of
the book of Proverbs.

00:18:23.550 --> 00:18:27.490 align:middle line:10%
"Wisdom hath built
her house," they said.

00:18:27.490 --> 00:18:29.220 align:middle line:10%
And of course,
Wisdom's house can

00:18:29.220 --> 00:18:31.490 align:middle line:10%
be interpreted on many levels.

00:18:31.490 --> 00:18:34.930 align:middle line:84%
At one level, Wisdom's
house is our body,

00:18:34.930 --> 00:18:37.670 align:middle line:90%
and Sophia dwells within us.

00:18:37.670 --> 00:18:40.900 align:middle line:90%
Her throne is our body.

00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:41.840 align:middle line:90%
Now think about that.

00:18:41.840 --> 00:18:45.390 align:middle line:84%
Your body is actually the
throne of this divine light

00:18:45.390 --> 00:18:47.200 align:middle line:90%
and this divine energy.

00:18:47.200 --> 00:18:49.360 align:middle line:84%
So here we see
Sophia, once again,

00:18:49.360 --> 00:18:53.910 align:middle line:84%
clothed in red, winged,
with Mary holding the baby

00:18:53.910 --> 00:18:56.180 align:middle line:84%
Jesus and John the
Baptist on either side.

00:18:56.180 --> 00:18:58.580 align:middle line:84%
Mary and Jesus are
shown in these images

00:18:58.580 --> 00:19:00.320 align:middle line:84%
because they were
the two-- or, excuse

00:19:00.320 --> 00:19:02.870 align:middle line:84%
me, Mary and John the Baptist
are shown because they were

00:19:02.870 --> 00:19:06.640 align:middle line:84%
the two most important people
in the mission of Jesus,

00:19:06.640 --> 00:19:12.090 align:middle line:84%
the messenger sent here to
awaken us and to enlighten us.

00:19:12.090 --> 00:19:16.160 align:middle line:10%
Here's a beautiful painting
by Sano di Piedro showing

00:19:16.160 --> 00:19:18.870 align:middle line:10%
Wisdom emanating from God.

00:19:18.870 --> 00:19:21.060 align:middle line:10%
And we look at this image
here, and we readily

00:19:21.060 --> 00:19:23.010 align:middle line:10%
think, OK, I see the stars.

00:19:23.010 --> 00:19:25.030 align:middle line:10%
We see God in another realm.

00:19:25.030 --> 00:19:28.940 align:middle line:10%
And Wisdom being pushed
into the material realm

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:31.920 align:middle line:10%
as if through a
portal, a gateway,

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:34.890 align:middle line:10%
a wormhole-- very
interesting idea.

00:19:34.890 --> 00:19:39.190 align:middle line:84%
Because what links
dimensions but a wormhole?

00:19:39.190 --> 00:19:41.860 align:middle line:10%
Here we see, again,
Wisdom clothed

00:19:41.860 --> 00:19:44.890 align:middle line:10%
in royal garments with
the crown and scepter

00:19:44.890 --> 00:19:47.930 align:middle line:10%
as she sits on a throne
as the personification

00:19:47.930 --> 00:19:49.870 align:middle line:10%
of the Wisdom of God.

00:19:49.870 --> 00:19:53.700 align:middle line:10%
This is a particular favorite,
because we see, again, Wisdom

00:19:53.700 --> 00:19:57.840 align:middle line:10%
is winged, radiant,
wearing the red robe.

00:19:57.840 --> 00:19:59.830 align:middle line:10%
And I emphasize the
red robe because we're

00:19:59.830 --> 00:20:02.540 align:middle line:10%
going to see that come
back up, that imagery come

00:20:02.540 --> 00:20:07.150 align:middle line:10%
back up in a really powerful
place here in a moment.

00:20:07.150 --> 00:20:10.000 align:middle line:10%
Continuing, now we see
another example here

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:13.040 align:middle line:10%
with Wisdom with
Jesus just behind,

00:20:13.040 --> 00:20:16.490 align:middle line:10%
indicating that he is also
from this otherworldly,

00:20:16.490 --> 00:20:19.250 align:middle line:10%
celestial realm, or
other dimensional realm.

00:20:19.250 --> 00:20:23.000 align:middle line:10%
Another example, also
from Russia, same imagery.

00:20:23.000 --> 00:20:25.290 align:middle line:10%
So we see it over
and over again.

00:20:25.290 --> 00:20:28.840 align:middle line:10%
But I particularly like this
one because we see, of course,

00:20:28.840 --> 00:20:31.990 align:middle line:10%
Wisdom with the red
robe, winged, Mary,

00:20:31.990 --> 00:20:33.850 align:middle line:10%
John the Baptist on either side.

00:20:33.850 --> 00:20:36.420 align:middle line:10%
But look at the
detail above Jesus.

00:20:36.420 --> 00:20:38.910 align:middle line:10%
Now this is always
fascinating to me

00:20:38.910 --> 00:20:42.290 align:middle line:10%
in Christian art when
I see above Sophia,

00:20:42.290 --> 00:20:46.940 align:middle line:10%
or any other figure, angels
holding this banner of stars.

00:20:46.940 --> 00:20:48.640 align:middle line:10%
The reason that's
so intriguing to me

00:20:48.640 --> 00:20:53.100 align:middle line:10%
is because what it symbolizes
is an other dimensional realm.

00:20:53.100 --> 00:20:57.380 align:middle line:10%
This is with these artists are
expressing the idea of a realm

00:20:57.380 --> 00:21:02.310 align:middle line:10%
beyond the stars, a light
beyond light, something that

00:21:02.310 --> 00:21:05.890 align:middle line:10%
is almost unfathomable
to the human imagination,

00:21:05.890 --> 00:21:08.080 align:middle line:10%
and is shown very simply
and elegantly here

00:21:08.080 --> 00:21:12.020 align:middle line:10%
as this banner of stars that
is unrolled by the angels.

00:21:12.020 --> 00:21:15.110 align:middle line:84%
Because of course,
these angelic beings

00:21:15.110 --> 00:21:17.580 align:middle line:84%
possess the power
of the universe.

00:21:17.580 --> 00:21:19.890 align:middle line:84%
They can roll up a
dimension into a roll

00:21:19.890 --> 00:21:23.580 align:middle line:84%
and unroll it and step through
that gateway and travel

00:21:23.580 --> 00:21:24.520 align:middle line:90%
interdimensionally.

00:21:24.520 --> 00:21:27.460 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, this is
something that all of us

00:21:27.460 --> 00:21:30.880 align:middle line:84%
are said to have the capability
of doing or attaining

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:32.140 align:middle line:90%
these capabilities.

00:21:32.140 --> 00:21:34.290 align:middle line:90%
So think about that.

00:21:34.290 --> 00:21:36.680 align:middle line:10%
So, side by side
example here of a couple

00:21:36.680 --> 00:21:39.332 align:middle line:10%
of these images of
Wisdom enthroned

00:21:39.332 --> 00:21:41.040 align:middle line:10%
and in the one on the
right in particular

00:21:41.040 --> 00:21:44.200 align:middle line:10%
with the banner of stars
above, representing

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.322 align:middle line:10%
the other dimensions.

00:21:45.322 --> 00:21:47.030 align:middle line:10%
One of our favorite
paintings, of course,

00:21:47.030 --> 00:21:51.000 align:middle line:10%
is Constantino Brumidi,
who painted Wisdom holding

00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:55.210 align:middle line:10%
her staff of arcanum in
the United States capital,

00:21:55.210 --> 00:21:57.250 align:middle line:10%
the US Capitol temple.

00:21:57.250 --> 00:21:59.400 align:middle line:84%
So of course Wisdom
is going to be there.

00:21:59.400 --> 00:22:00.360 align:middle line:90%
She's present.

00:22:00.360 --> 00:22:02.960 align:middle line:84%
She's guiding the
founding fathers

00:22:02.960 --> 00:22:06.180 align:middle line:84%
and is an inspiration to
the founding fathers, who

00:22:06.180 --> 00:22:08.790 align:middle line:84%
must have understood
this idea of the divine

00:22:08.790 --> 00:22:12.520 align:middle line:84%
spark when they expressed
their idea of creating

00:22:12.520 --> 00:22:17.160 align:middle line:84%
a psychological space, America,
where souls could attain

00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:20.930 align:middle line:84%
ultimate wisdom and their
ultimate capability.

00:22:20.930 --> 00:22:23.810 align:middle line:10%
Through her desire
to know the Father,

00:22:23.810 --> 00:22:27.230 align:middle line:10%
Wisdom, Sophia, was
cast out of the Pleroma,

00:22:27.230 --> 00:22:29.820 align:middle line:10%
the Gnostic heaven,
again possibly

00:22:29.820 --> 00:22:32.830 align:middle line:10%
the center of the galaxy, at
least in some people's views.

00:22:32.830 --> 00:22:37.070 align:middle line:10%
And I like that, because it
localizes in our imagination

00:22:37.070 --> 00:22:39.360 align:middle line:10%
the location of God's throne.

00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:43.010 align:middle line:84%
And her desire gave birth to
God, who created the material

00:22:43.010 --> 00:22:47.050 align:middle line:84%
world, again showing this
overlap between the immaterial

00:22:47.050 --> 00:22:48.820 align:middle line:90%
and the material world.

00:22:48.820 --> 00:22:51.630 align:middle line:84%
Although she was eventually
restored to the Pleroma,

00:22:51.630 --> 00:22:55.870 align:middle line:84%
bits of her divinity remain
in the material world.

00:22:55.870 --> 00:22:58.270 align:middle line:90%
These are the divine sparks.

00:22:58.270 --> 00:23:01.300 align:middle line:10%
So here we see Sophia from
a 16th century painting

00:23:01.300 --> 00:23:03.150 align:middle line:10%
from the "Book of
Wonders," shown

00:23:03.150 --> 00:23:06.900 align:middle line:10%
as a feminine angel
holding the trumpet.

00:23:06.900 --> 00:23:10.020 align:middle line:10%
Now look at that trumpet
and the detail here.

00:23:10.020 --> 00:23:13.660 align:middle line:84%
And just see if you can pull
out the wormhole symbolism,

00:23:13.660 --> 00:23:14.570 align:middle line:90%
as I can.

00:23:14.570 --> 00:23:17.570 align:middle line:84%
We have this bell-shaped
opening here.

00:23:17.570 --> 00:23:21.190 align:middle line:84%
We have this tube and the
opening coming out here.

00:23:21.190 --> 00:23:24.450 align:middle line:84%
Maybe, maybe not, is what
the artist had in mind here.

00:23:24.450 --> 00:23:26.080 align:middle line:84%
But from a modern
perspective, we

00:23:26.080 --> 00:23:29.860 align:middle line:84%
can look at that image and
say, that's a wormhole.

00:23:29.860 --> 00:23:32.320 align:middle line:84%
And again, "Wisdom
has built their house.

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:36.790 align:middle line:84%
She has set up her seven
pillars," the famed seven

00:23:36.790 --> 00:23:38.570 align:middle line:90%
pillars of wisdom.

00:23:38.570 --> 00:23:41.070 align:middle line:10%
And when we're looking at
various interpretations

00:23:41.070 --> 00:23:42.750 align:middle line:10%
of that statement,
as in this example

00:23:42.750 --> 00:23:45.710 align:middle line:10%
here from Kiev of "Saint
Sophia The Wisdom of God,"

00:23:45.710 --> 00:23:50.150 align:middle line:10%
we see Sophia standing
amongst the seven pillars.

00:23:50.150 --> 00:23:51.670 align:middle line:10%
And of course, as
we look at this,

00:23:51.670 --> 00:23:54.970 align:middle line:10%
we see the seven pillars
are externalized.

00:23:54.970 --> 00:23:59.850 align:middle line:10%
We have Sophia, the baby
Christ in her heart chakra,

00:23:59.850 --> 00:24:04.350 align:middle line:10%
radiant, exploding into light,
a radiating light with the seven

00:24:04.350 --> 00:24:07.280 align:middle line:10%
pillars all around her.

00:24:07.280 --> 00:24:09.970 align:middle line:10%
And now, once again, when we
look at an image such as this

00:24:09.970 --> 00:24:14.420 align:middle line:10%
and we see Sophia with her open
heart chakra and her hands out,

00:24:14.420 --> 00:24:18.380 align:middle line:10%
it's a good thing to do to
mirror that image, to reflect

00:24:18.380 --> 00:24:21.220 align:middle line:10%
what you're seeing as well as
contemplating and meditating

00:24:21.220 --> 00:24:22.310 align:middle line:10%
on this image.

00:24:22.310 --> 00:24:24.620 align:middle line:84%
So if you put up your
hands to your screen,

00:24:24.620 --> 00:24:27.130 align:middle line:84%
you can reflect
the energy that's

00:24:27.130 --> 00:24:29.750 align:middle line:84%
emanating from Sophia
at this moment.

00:24:29.750 --> 00:24:32.210 align:middle line:10%
That is the intention
behind images

00:24:32.210 --> 00:24:35.260 align:middle line:10%
such as this, is that we're to
use them as mirrors in order

00:24:35.260 --> 00:24:39.060 align:middle line:10%
to bring this divine light
and wisdom into our own life.

00:24:39.060 --> 00:24:43.940 align:middle line:10%
And in a sense, then,
Sophia becomes the messenger

00:24:43.940 --> 00:24:47.720 align:middle line:10%
who has stepped through
the portal of your screen

00:24:47.720 --> 00:24:52.570 align:middle line:10%
and is now here to illuminate
and awaken your consciousness.

00:24:52.570 --> 00:24:57.080 align:middle line:10%
So take a moment here to
absorb this light and vibration

00:24:57.080 --> 00:24:58.820 align:middle line:10%
of wisdom coming from Sophia.

00:24:58.820 --> 00:25:01.580 align:middle line:10%


00:25:01.580 --> 00:25:03.260 align:middle line:10%
And as you're doing
so, once again

00:25:03.260 --> 00:25:08.750 align:middle line:10%
note that she is robed
in her red cloak.

00:25:08.750 --> 00:25:11.820 align:middle line:84%
Here's God above,
sending or beaming

00:25:11.820 --> 00:25:15.160 align:middle line:84%
this ray of divine light
and love into Sophia

00:25:15.160 --> 00:25:16.840 align:middle line:90%
from another worldly realm.

00:25:16.840 --> 00:25:19.420 align:middle line:84%
We see the radiant dove
of the Holy Spirit,

00:25:19.420 --> 00:25:22.230 align:middle line:84%
symbolizing the
cosmic vibration.

00:25:22.230 --> 00:25:25.640 align:middle line:84%
And finally, the whole
scene comes together.

00:25:25.640 --> 00:25:27.070 align:middle line:10%
We count the steps here.

00:25:27.070 --> 00:25:31.520 align:middle line:10%
We go one, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, again,

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:33.820 align:middle line:10%
all good children go to heaven.

00:25:33.820 --> 00:25:38.770 align:middle line:84%
And it looks as if Sophia is in
some otherworldly temple here.

00:25:38.770 --> 00:25:41.580 align:middle line:84%
And we feel as if we
can ascend the steps

00:25:41.580 --> 00:25:45.890 align:middle line:84%
and just enter into this divine
realm and stand beside her.

00:25:45.890 --> 00:25:49.020 align:middle line:84%
But another perspective here
is that those seven pillars

00:25:49.020 --> 00:25:51.060 align:middle line:90%
are actually within us.

00:25:51.060 --> 00:25:53.330 align:middle line:90%
They represent our chakras.

00:25:53.330 --> 00:25:53.890 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:25:53.890 --> 00:25:56.760 align:middle line:84%
The ladder, or stairway,
to heaven within us,

00:25:56.760 --> 00:25:59.160 align:middle line:90%
the seven pillars of wisdom.

00:25:59.160 --> 00:26:03.180 align:middle line:84%
And by activating the chakras,
we illuminate our consciousness

00:26:03.180 --> 00:26:05.995 align:middle line:84%
and become fully
functioning beings.

00:26:05.995 --> 00:26:08.520 align:middle line:90%


00:26:08.520 --> 00:26:12.190 align:middle line:10%
Another example, an icon
of Sophia, the holy Wisdom,

00:26:12.190 --> 00:26:14.110 align:middle line:10%
surrounded by the seven pillars.

00:26:14.110 --> 00:26:16.500 align:middle line:10%
It was particularly
in Russia coming out

00:26:16.500 --> 00:26:18.170 align:middle line:10%
of the Eastern
tradition where we

00:26:18.170 --> 00:26:23.140 align:middle line:10%
see images such as this that
are extraordinarily empowering.

00:26:23.140 --> 00:26:26.950 align:middle line:84%
And we're always stepping up
our vibration or our frequency.

00:26:26.950 --> 00:26:28.760 align:middle line:84%
We see the Hebrew
high priest here,

00:26:28.760 --> 00:26:30.880 align:middle line:84%
the Israelite high
priest, wearing the breast

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:33.240 align:middle line:84%
plate of righteousness,
triggering us

00:26:33.240 --> 00:26:35.540 align:middle line:84%
that this is a path
of righteousness.

00:26:35.540 --> 00:26:38.070 align:middle line:84%
And righteous simply
means to follow

00:26:38.070 --> 00:26:41.340 align:middle line:84%
the good path, or
the godly path.

00:26:41.340 --> 00:26:43.970 align:middle line:84%
We all know those
self-righteous types.

00:26:43.970 --> 00:26:45.240 align:middle line:90%
That's not our goal.

00:26:45.240 --> 00:26:48.870 align:middle line:84%
But our goal certainly is
to become righteous beings,

00:26:48.870 --> 00:26:53.970 align:middle line:84%
to be on the path of doing the
right thing with right life,

00:26:53.970 --> 00:26:57.530 align:middle line:84%
right thought, right
action, right intention.

00:26:57.530 --> 00:26:59.460 align:middle line:84%
That's part of the
Buddhist Eightfold

00:26:59.460 --> 00:27:02.770 align:middle line:84%
Path of righteousness
that we're describing here

00:27:02.770 --> 00:27:06.540 align:middle line:84%
and suggests an overlap
between these Gnostic,

00:27:06.540 --> 00:27:09.120 align:middle line:90%
or enlightened, traditions.

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:13.370 align:middle line:84%
Our behavior, our actions,
are the key in Earth life.

00:27:13.370 --> 00:27:17.140 align:middle line:84%
I mean, how do you behave
when no one is looking

00:27:17.140 --> 00:27:18.790 align:middle line:90%
is not a rhetorical question.

00:27:18.790 --> 00:27:22.450 align:middle line:84%
Because someone
always is looking.

00:27:22.450 --> 00:27:24.760 align:middle line:84%
Your divine self,
your higher self,

00:27:24.760 --> 00:27:27.520 align:middle line:84%
is always watching
and saying, William, I

00:27:27.520 --> 00:27:30.600 align:middle line:84%
know you could have done a
lot better in that situation.

00:27:30.600 --> 00:27:33.200 align:middle line:84%
And most often we
don't get to redo.

00:27:33.200 --> 00:27:36.480 align:middle line:84%
So it's always best to have
our highest intention in mind

00:27:36.480 --> 00:27:40.490 align:middle line:84%
and make sure our actions
are on the right path.

00:27:40.490 --> 00:27:43.580 align:middle line:84%
Most of us, unfortunately,
in the Earth plane--

00:27:43.580 --> 00:27:46.100 align:middle line:84%
this isn't a judgment
or an incrimination.

00:27:46.100 --> 00:27:48.660 align:middle line:84%
But most of us
remain unconscious

00:27:48.660 --> 00:27:51.050 align:middle line:84%
of the original spark
within us and certainly

00:27:51.050 --> 00:27:52.840 align:middle line:90%
the messenger within us.

00:27:52.840 --> 00:27:54.810 align:middle line:84%
We tend to externalize,
and we feel

00:27:54.810 --> 00:27:58.970 align:middle line:84%
like there's a savior being
or some other figure that's

00:27:58.970 --> 00:28:02.650 align:middle line:84%
going to come into our life
and make everything OK.

00:28:02.650 --> 00:28:05.330 align:middle line:84%
And we don't take that
responsibility for ourselves

00:28:05.330 --> 00:28:09.530 align:middle line:84%
when the Gnostics were clearly
telling us, hey, it's up to us.

00:28:09.530 --> 00:28:12.690 align:middle line:84%
It's up to you to take
that first right step

00:28:12.690 --> 00:28:14.910 align:middle line:90%
and stay on that right path.

00:28:14.910 --> 00:28:18.440 align:middle line:84%
So what we have to do is
become conscious of this aspect

00:28:18.440 --> 00:28:22.190 align:middle line:84%
of ourselves during an
awakening experience.

00:28:22.190 --> 00:28:25.000 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes that's a
moment of synchronicity.

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:27.160 align:middle line:84%
We've probably all had
that experience, where

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:30.120 align:middle line:84%
we're driving down the
road and all of a sudden,

00:28:30.120 --> 00:28:31.380 align:middle line:90%
a voice says, oh, no.

00:28:31.380 --> 00:28:33.960 align:middle line:84%
You're about to turn right,
but you've got to turn left.

00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:35.731 align:middle line:90%
And we follow that guidance.

00:28:35.731 --> 00:28:37.480 align:middle line:84%
And then we look to
the right, and there's

00:28:37.480 --> 00:28:39.770 align:middle line:90%
a cataclysmic event that occurs.

00:28:39.770 --> 00:28:42.840 align:middle line:84%
And we wonder, gosh, where
did that voice come from?

00:28:42.840 --> 00:28:44.410 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's our
higher self that's

00:28:44.410 --> 00:28:47.620 align:middle line:84%
always sitting right
beside us all along.

00:28:47.620 --> 00:28:49.480 align:middle line:90%
It has that bird's eye view.

00:28:49.480 --> 00:28:50.980 align:middle line:90%
It can see on down the road.

00:28:50.980 --> 00:28:53.220 align:middle line:90%
It can see the future.

00:28:53.220 --> 00:28:56.270 align:middle line:84%
And if we listen to that
voice and consistently listen

00:28:56.270 --> 00:28:59.830 align:middle line:84%
to that voice, we're going
to avoid many obstacles.

00:28:59.830 --> 00:29:02.320 align:middle line:84%
But not only that, it's
where it's leading us

00:29:02.320 --> 00:29:06.330 align:middle line:84%
is to that place of the light
and illumination and awakening.

00:29:06.330 --> 00:29:08.530 align:middle line:90%
That's its ultimate intention.

00:29:08.530 --> 00:29:11.040 align:middle line:10%
And that's where we
want to go is that place

00:29:11.040 --> 00:29:13.650 align:middle line:10%
of light and illumination.

00:29:13.650 --> 00:29:18.010 align:middle line:10%
Every person has within
them a higher ego,

00:29:18.010 --> 00:29:21.260 align:middle line:10%
or portion of the cosmic soul.

00:29:21.260 --> 00:29:24.850 align:middle line:10%
The Sufis and the Kabbalists
called it the divine spark.

00:29:24.850 --> 00:29:27.550 align:middle line:10%
And they believe it's
contained or imprisoned

00:29:27.550 --> 00:29:29.810 align:middle line:10%
within the human body.

00:29:29.810 --> 00:29:33.500 align:middle line:10%
My good friend, an artist
Mr. Dana Augustine,

00:29:33.500 --> 00:29:36.380 align:middle line:10%
visualized the divine
spark for us in this way,

00:29:36.380 --> 00:29:39.250 align:middle line:10%
showing a humanoid
shape, a human female,

00:29:39.250 --> 00:29:43.800 align:middle line:10%
in an almond-shaped gateway,
a mandorla, surrounded

00:29:43.800 --> 00:29:46.490 align:middle line:10%
by rainbow-colored
light, or fire,

00:29:46.490 --> 00:29:49.350 align:middle line:10%
with this golden
kernel surrounding it.

00:29:49.350 --> 00:29:51.680 align:middle line:10%
We can see this based
on Gnostic texts.

00:29:51.680 --> 00:29:54.130 align:middle line:84%
And this is how they
described the divine spark

00:29:54.130 --> 00:29:56.180 align:middle line:90%
as that golden kernel.

00:29:56.180 --> 00:29:58.500 align:middle line:10%
In fact, the Gnostics
teach that who we are

00:29:58.500 --> 00:30:01.460 align:middle line:10%
and what it is that is
enlightened within us--

00:30:01.460 --> 00:30:05.710 align:middle line:10%
or perfected is the term
they also prefer to use,

00:30:05.710 --> 00:30:09.690 align:middle line:10%
in the alchemical tradition,
that is-- is a solar drop,

00:30:09.690 --> 00:30:13.660 align:middle line:10%
an immortal pearl, an
indestructible drop, a seed

00:30:13.660 --> 00:30:17.200 align:middle line:10%
atom that is perceived by
some as a drop of molten gold

00:30:17.200 --> 00:30:19.140 align:middle line:10%
or stardust.

00:30:19.140 --> 00:30:21.690 align:middle line:10%
Remember that Joni Mitchell
song, "you are stardust,

00:30:21.690 --> 00:30:22.770 align:middle line:10%
you are golden?"

00:30:22.770 --> 00:30:26.260 align:middle line:84%
That's an absolute,
literal Gnostic truth

00:30:26.260 --> 00:30:31.210 align:middle line:84%
that she's offering, a true gem
she's offering in that song.

00:30:31.210 --> 00:30:34.430 align:middle line:90%
It is the inner light within us.

00:30:34.430 --> 00:30:36.500 align:middle line:84%
So perhaps you want
to take a moment

00:30:36.500 --> 00:30:38.810 align:middle line:84%
to meditate on
this image as well.

00:30:38.810 --> 00:30:42.270 align:middle line:84%
And take it into your being
and reflect on, wait a minute,

00:30:42.270 --> 00:30:45.770 align:middle line:90%
this body is not who I truly am.

00:30:45.770 --> 00:30:51.230 align:middle line:84%
This divine spark, this immortal
pearl, this spec of stardust

00:30:51.230 --> 00:30:53.570 align:middle line:90%
is who I truly am.

00:30:53.570 --> 00:30:56.310 align:middle line:84%
And that is what will
carry me from incarnation

00:30:56.310 --> 00:31:00.410 align:middle line:84%
to incarnation on my
path of reincarnation.

00:31:00.410 --> 00:31:03.000 align:middle line:84%
Various names for this
transcendent aspect of our self

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:03.980 align:middle line:90%
are offered.

00:31:03.980 --> 00:31:06.620 align:middle line:84%
That's called Our
Original Luminous Nature

00:31:06.620 --> 00:31:10.300 align:middle line:84%
in Chinese Manichaeanism, the
Living Self, the Luminous Self.

00:31:10.300 --> 00:31:12.160 align:middle line:90%
Mana.

00:31:12.160 --> 00:31:14.460 align:middle line:84%
It's also referred to
as the Spirit in Us,

00:31:14.460 --> 00:31:17.460 align:middle line:84%
the Inner Man, the
Spark, the Divine Spark,

00:31:17.460 --> 00:31:21.430 align:middle line:84%
the Seed of Light, all
perfectly appropriate terms

00:31:21.430 --> 00:31:24.820 align:middle line:84%
for describing this
true essence within us.

00:31:24.820 --> 00:31:29.100 align:middle line:84%
The Bible alludes to the idea
of a divine spark within us.

00:31:29.100 --> 00:31:32.030 align:middle line:84%
Genesis 1:26 teaches
that every human being

00:31:32.030 --> 00:31:34.970 align:middle line:90%
possesses the image of God.

00:31:34.970 --> 00:31:38.630 align:middle line:84%
Ecclesiastes declares
that God has set eternity

00:31:38.630 --> 00:31:41.260 align:middle line:90%
in the hearts of men.

00:31:41.260 --> 00:31:44.160 align:middle line:84%
That might even suggest
a location of the divine

00:31:44.160 --> 00:31:46.140 align:middle line:90%
spark within us.

00:31:46.140 --> 00:31:48.750 align:middle line:84%
Do we have that aspect of
ourselves in our hearts,

00:31:48.750 --> 00:31:51.920 align:middle line:84%
or is it located in
another part of our body?

00:31:51.920 --> 00:31:56.240 align:middle line:84%
In Luke, Jesus proclaims the
kingdom of God is within you.

00:31:56.240 --> 00:32:00.500 align:middle line:84%
It's spread out all around
us, and we just don't see it.

00:32:00.500 --> 00:32:03.460 align:middle line:84%
We're blinded by
the material light.

00:32:03.460 --> 00:32:06.230 align:middle line:84%
We think this is
all there is, and we

00:32:06.230 --> 00:32:10.340 align:middle line:84%
stay focused on this very
narrow frequency spectrum,

00:32:10.340 --> 00:32:13.015 align:middle line:84%
very seldom wandering
out beyond it.

00:32:13.015 --> 00:32:15.390 align:middle line:84%
But that's where the
divine self lives

00:32:15.390 --> 00:32:18.600 align:middle line:84%
is on the periphery,
on the perimeter,

00:32:18.600 --> 00:32:21.170 align:middle line:90%
beyond the narrow way.

00:32:21.170 --> 00:32:22.990 align:middle line:84%
That's what we're
called upon to do

00:32:22.990 --> 00:32:27.120 align:middle line:84%
is to expand our consciousness,
to expand our imagination,

00:32:27.120 --> 00:32:29.380 align:middle line:84%
to encompass the
immaterial realm

00:32:29.380 --> 00:32:32.380 align:middle line:84%
and realize that all, everything
that we see that's material

00:32:32.380 --> 00:32:36.030 align:middle line:84%
actually originates in
the immaterial realm.

00:32:36.030 --> 00:32:39.250 align:middle line:84%
The Bible teaches that
every human being possesses

00:32:39.250 --> 00:32:42.500 align:middle line:84%
an immaterial soul
spirit, a divine spark.

00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:45.160 align:middle line:84%
And it is this part
of us that connects

00:32:45.160 --> 00:32:49.570 align:middle line:84%
with God-- very
powerful teaching.

00:32:49.570 --> 00:32:51.620 align:middle line:84%
It's no exaggeration
to say, actually,

00:32:51.620 --> 00:32:55.520 align:middle line:84%
that the discovery of this
transcendent, inner aspect

00:32:55.520 --> 00:32:57.770 align:middle line:84%
of our self, or this
principle within us,

00:32:57.770 --> 00:33:01.590 align:middle line:84%
and the supreme concern
about its destiny

00:33:01.590 --> 00:33:04.220 align:middle line:84%
is the very center
of gnostic belief.

00:33:04.220 --> 00:33:07.090 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it's the aim
of all of our lives

00:33:07.090 --> 00:33:08.990 align:middle line:90%
is to make that connection.

00:33:08.990 --> 00:33:10.330 align:middle line:90%
Remember the Hymn of the Pearl.

00:33:10.330 --> 00:33:12.190 align:middle line:90%
It says, remember who you are.

00:33:12.190 --> 00:33:14.480 align:middle line:84%
Remember that immortal
pearl within you.

00:33:14.480 --> 00:33:17.200 align:middle line:84%
Snatch it away from the
dragon that guards it.

