00:33:23.750 --> 00:33:26.090 align:middle line:84%
The divine spark,
the Gnostics teach,

00:33:26.090 --> 00:33:30.050 align:middle line:84%
is what grows the
vehicles for incarnation,

00:33:30.050 --> 00:33:33.127 align:middle line:84%
in particular the human
body, but the Gnostics,

00:33:33.127 --> 00:33:35.710 align:middle line:84%
like the ancient Egyptians, seem
to believe that we could even

00:33:35.710 --> 00:33:39.000 align:middle line:84%
incarnate as cats and
other animals-- whatever

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:42.630 align:middle line:84%
