whatever it needs to learn.

00:33:42.630 --> 00:33:45.390 align:middle line:84%
But let's just focus
on the human body now

00:33:45.390 --> 00:33:48.100 align:middle line:84%
and this teaching
that the divine spark

00:33:48.100 --> 00:33:54.240 align:middle line:84%
is what grows our physical body
as a vehicle for incarnation.

00:33:54.240 --> 00:33:56.940 align:middle line:84%
All the individual souls,
or divine particles

00:33:56.940 --> 00:34:00.950 align:middle line:84%
of primordial light, constitute
the great universal soul.

00:34:00.950 --> 00:34:02.010 align:middle line:90%
We all have one.

00:34:02.010 --> 00:34:05.690 align:middle line:84%
And it is what has created
our physical body, which

00:34:05.690 --> 00:34:07.700 align:middle line:84%
means our physical
body is always

00:34:07.700 --> 00:34:09.909 align:middle line:90%
connected to all that is.

00:34:09.909 --> 00:34:14.280 align:middle line:84%
We just have to take the
blinders off, take off

00:34:14.280 --> 00:34:19.620 align:middle line:84%
the lens of Earth life and
awaken to the greater cosmos.

00:34:19.620 --> 00:34:22.412 align:middle line:84%
Where is that divine
spark located in the body?

00:34:22.412 --> 00:34:23.870 align:middle line:84%
Well, in some
traditions, they want

00:34:23.870 --> 00:34:27.520 align:middle line:84%
