the divine spark is located

00:34:37.310 --> 00:34:40.030 align:middle line:84%
in the sacrum bone,
which they refer

00:34:40.030 --> 00:34:45.780 align:middle line:84%
to as the sacred or holy
bone, the resurrection bone.

00:34:45.780 --> 00:34:47.880 align:middle line:84%
