luz, or almond.

00:34:47.880 --> 00:34:52.151 align:middle line:84%
And they refer to it as a
doorway to the other world.

00:34:52.151 --> 00:34:53.900 align:middle line:84%
And they tell us that
it is this bone that

00:34:53.900 --> 00:34:57.080 align:middle line:90%
