in the heart chakra.

00:35:02.050 --> 00:35:03.180 align:middle line:90%
Well, that makes sense.

00:35:03.180 --> 00:35:04.840 align:middle line:10%
But the truth of
the matter is here

00:35:04.840 --> 00:35:06.460 align:middle line:10%
is that-- or, the
fact of the matter

00:35:06.460 --> 00:35:10.590 align:middle line:10%
is that our body is manifested
by this divine aspect

00:35:10.590 --> 00:35:13.020 align:middle line:10%
of ourselves according
to the Gnostics.

00:35:13.020 --> 00:35:14.980 align:middle line:10%
Bones, fascia,
connective tissue,

00:35:14.980 --> 00:35:17.730 align:middle line:10%
