crystalline substance.

00:35:20.630 --> 00:35:24.380 align:middle line:10%
It's like a crystal on a radio
set that's used by the divine

00:35:24.380 --> 00:35:27.460 align:middle line:10%
spark to tune in to
these spiritual or divine

00:35:27.460 --> 00:35:28.966 align:middle line:10%
frequencies.

00:35:28.966 --> 00:35:31.590 align:middle line:10%
The interesting thing about the
crystals and crystal structures

00:35:31.590 --> 00:35:35.550 align:middle line:10%
