for quantum phenomena.

00:35:35.550 --> 00:35:39.240 align:middle line:10%
And ultimately it is through
this crystalline aspect

00:35:39.240 --> 00:35:41.210 align:middle line:10%
of ourselves that
we're able to tune

00:35:41.210 --> 00:35:44.880 align:middle line:10%
in to these divine
vibrations and reconnect

00:35:44.880 --> 00:35:49.160 align:middle line:10%
with our true, divine
self in the Pleroma.

00:35:49.160 --> 00:35:53.090 align:middle line:84%
