to act as information gathering

00:36:03.110 --> 00:36:06.870 align:middle line:84%
equipment, as well as Earthly
transportation vehicles and as

00:36:06.870 --> 00:36:10.270 align:middle line:84%
energy harvesting and
processing devices.

00:36:10.270 --> 00:36:13.490 align:middle line:84%
E.J. Gold has a beautiful book
called "The Human Biological

00:36:13.490 --> 00:36:15.520 align:middle line:90%
Transformational Apparatus."

