And what we are
charged with doing

00:36:34.300 --> 00:36:37.060 align:middle line:84%
is taking our emphasis
off the physical

00:36:37.060 --> 00:36:40.770 align:middle line:84%
and putting it on the
immaterial, divine aspect

00:36:40.770 --> 00:36:42.486 align:middle line:90%
within.

00:36:42.486 --> 00:36:44.110 align:middle line:84%
And so here we are,
once again, looking

00:36:44.110 --> 00:36:47.190 align:middle line:84%
