Fine Arts in Boston.

00:43:23.610 --> 00:43:27.360 align:middle line:10%
What we see here is what's
described as the Maya First

00:43:27.360 --> 00:43:28.600 align:middle line:10%
Father.

00:43:28.600 --> 00:43:31.200 align:middle line:84%
The Maya depicted on
their funerary ceramics

00:43:31.200 --> 00:43:35.540 align:middle line:84%
