00:43:47.280 --> 00:43:48.640 align:middle line:90%
this idea of resurrection.

00:43:48.640 --> 00:43:51.100 align:middle line:84%
And they would, in life,
create these plates

00:43:51.100 --> 00:43:53.390 align:middle line:84%
